
facebook_exceptions

A Rails plugin for rendering application errors directly within Facebook.

== License

Copyright (c) 2007 Cloudburst, LLC, released under the AFL 3.0.

== Requirements

* Edge Rails

= Usage

== Installation

Run the following command in the root of your Rails app:
  script/plugin install svn://rubyforge.org/var/svn/fauna/facebook_exceptions/trunk

There is no gem version. 

= Extras

== Sample

http://blog.evanweaver.com/files/facebook_exceptions_small.png

== Troubleshooting

If the exception view only works on the first request, make sure that ApplicationController is not marked as <tt>unloadable</tt>.

== Reporting problems

* http://rubyforge.org/forum/forum.php?forum_id=15872

Patches and contributions are very welcome. Please note that contributors are required to assign copyright for their additions to Cloudburst, LLC.

== Further resources

* http://blog.evanweaver.com/articles/2007/07/13/developing-a-facebook-app-locally
